txt.en:
Here's the list of things I seem to have lost with all this dancing and frivolity:

Foxglove's Teapot -- There is a lot of cooking going on around here. I was attracted by the smells, the last time I remember having this.

Foxglove's Parasol -- I remember speaking to old Gaffer around the time I noticed this was missing.

Foxglove's Wine -- I was comparing this bottle with the selections of summer wine out there.

Foxglove's Book -- I needed a quiet place to read and watch the festivities.

Foxglove's Twine -- Who would want an old ball of twine?
